STATE
v.
Salim Abdu GOULD. No. 91P14-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Sept. 24, 2015. Salim Abdu Gould, Windsor, for Gould, Salim Abdu. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of N.C. Valerie Mitchell Asbell, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 19th of August 2015 by Defendant of Leave to File Individual Writ of Certiorari:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 24th of September 2015."
